!@
This is a simple program that asks the user to enter eight numbers and prints
out the numbers' sum.  If the user enters a non-number, the program will
terminate with an error
#$


newList x val
<~								(8 (x length) <) while
x ("Please enter a number: " input) append x val

0 sum val
<~			((x length) range) in i for
((x (today i +) get) sum +) sum val

((sum str) "The sum of your numbers is " ++) print




